{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-people-page-js","path":"/speakers/david-gibbs","result":{"data":{"people":{"parent":{"html":"<h2>About</h2>\n<p>David Gibbs is a Research Associate in <a href=\"https://www.globalforestwatch.org/\">Global Forest Watch</a> (GFW) at the <a href=\"https://www.wri.org/\">World Resources Institute</a> (WRI). Although he works on a variety of forest monitoring projects, his primary focus has been modeling how forests store, emit, and sequester carbon globally. He has created a global model of greenhouse gas emissions and sequestration by forests from 2001 to 2021 at 30-meter resolution, as well as globally mapped potential rates of carbon sequestration from natural forest regeneration. David has also contributed to the New York Declaration on Forests annual progress assessment—which tracks global progress in stopping deforestation—since 2018 and assisted cities with including forests and trees in their greenhouse gas inventories. Before joining WRI, David was a research fellow at the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency and an environmental scientist at Tetra Tech, Inc.</p>"},"id":"da212b49-1133-5ff6-8169-eeefe8452ed6","title":"David Gibbs","company":"World Resources Institute","role":"GIS Research Associate","twitter":null,"pronouns":null,"avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/933e0041c1fd0a5950345a89ff3ad3f3/1b50a/david-gibbs.jpg","srcSet":"/static/933e0041c1fd0a5950345a89ff3ad3f3/c904d/david-gibbs.jpg 160w,\n/static/933e0041c1fd0a5950345a89ff3ad3f3/b95ad/david-gibbs.jpg 320w,\n/static/933e0041c1fd0a5950345a89ff3ad3f3/1b50a/david-gibbs.jpg 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/933e0041c1fd0a5950345a89ff3ad3f3/c6aca/david-gibbs.webp 160w,\n/static/933e0041c1fd0a5950345a89ff3ad3f3/0a0af/david-gibbs.webp 320w,\n/static/933e0041c1fd0a5950345a89ff3ad3f3/8ae69/david-gibbs.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":640,"height":640}}},"events":[{"role":"speakers","event":{"parent":{"html":"<p>Several big bets have been made on the ability of satellite data to improve carbon accounting. This panel will explore what is required for meaningful carbon accounting, where better earth data and better models will contribute, and what are their limitations.</p>"},"cId":"29-1130-carbon-accounting","title":"Meaningful Carbon Accounting","slug":"29-1130-carbon-accounting","type":"Session","room":"The North Hub","date":"2022-09-29 11:30","people":{"hosts":[],"moderators":[],"panelists":[],"facilitators":[],"speakers":[{"title":"Naikoa Aguilar Amuchastegui, PhD","slug":"naikoa-aguilaramuchastegui","group":"main"},{"title":"Carlos Silva, PhD","slug":"carlos-silva","group":"main"},{"title":"David Gibbs","slug":"david-gibbs","group":"main"},{"title":"Melissa Weitz","slug":"melissa-weitz","group":"main"}]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"david-gibbs"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2576411084","446613330","692872813"]}